The month is over, but the work is far from done. We’ve only started scratching the surface of all that goes #BehindtheB! Our commitment as a #BCorp is to keep on learning and working in community to fulfill the vision of an inclusive, equitable, and regenerative economy. So stay tuned for future updates about our journey and get in touch with us with your ideas and suggestions so we can build a better world today, together. 🤝 #GoodPop #PledgeGood #DoGoodGetGood

This month, step #BehindtheB… All throughout March, we’re swinging our doors wide open and inviting you to see what goes on #BehindtheB. Being a B Corp is something we’re really proud of, so for the next 30 days, we’ll be sharing what that means to us and why it matters. Come and find out what's Behind the B. #BCorpMonth #PurposeDrivenBusiness #BusinessForGood #BCorp #PledgeGood #DoGoodGetGood #GoodPop

We're on a mission to spread more GOOD! ✨ Help us by pledging to do a good deed on our website, and we'll match your pledge with a donation to our Pledge Good Partners! Link in bio. (You can pledge as often as you'd like and we'll donate each time. 😉) Read more about our regional partner @safeatx below. 🤝
.
⭐️ PLEDGE PARTNER HIGHLIGHT ⭐️
Our pledge good efforts and donations currently support The SAFE Alliance, which exists to stop abuse for everyone by serving the survivors of child abuse, sexual assault, trafficking, and domestic violence. Services include shelter and housing, face-to-face and digital support, prevention and education, and advocacy. 

Check out our Story to learn more about their upcoming event and more ways you can support! #PledgeGood #GoodPop #KeepAustinSAFE

Members of the GoodPop team have used their VTO this week to volunteer and collect goods to donate. Our current efforts are focused on helping those affected and those who are helping. 

If you’d like to help, please donate to the Kerr County Flood Relief Fund and TEXSAR.

Today we’re proud to launch the Good Food Collective! 🚀

We are a coalition of brands, organizations, and experts united in our mission to create a healthier future by driving transparency, higher standards, and empowering people to make informed, conscious food choices at the grocery store.

Meet the collective, check out our link in bio.
